Columbia expects the quantities to be provided through the new delivery points to be within its authorized level of
services. Also, Columbia estimates that the cost of installing the new taps to be approximately $150 per tap and that
project No. 1 to cost approximately $14,100, which would be reimbursed by Columbia Gas of Ohio. 


Comment date:

 March 14, 1994, in accordance with Standard Paragraph G at the end of this notice. 





